83	 * Helper function to split a string on a regex, but keep the delimiters.
84	 * This is required, because the JavaScript `.split()` method does not keep the delimiters,
85	 * and wrapping in a capturing group causes issues with existing capturing groups (due to nesting).
86	 * @param {string} text The text to split.
