- Uses both tokenizer and processor (TextImagePipelineConstructorArgs)
- Takes two inputs: image and question
- Uses task-specific tokenization with special tokens like `<s_docvqa><s_question>...<s_answer>`
- Decodes output and parses answer using regex pattern matching
